OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry today with some bright or
OL,6,Fsunny spells Skies will cloud over at
OL,7,Ftimes with an increasing risk of
OL,8,Fshowers in late afternoon. Feeling
OL,9,Fpleasant in the sunny spells.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FClouding over this evening
OL,12,Fwith showery outbreaks of rain.
OL,13,FStaying mild and frost free overnight
OL,14,Funder the thick blanket of cloud.
OL,15,
OL,16,CWednesday:FCloudy at first in the
OL,17,Fmorning with drizzly outbreaks.
OL,18,FGradually turning drier through the
OL,19,Fmorning with increasing bright or
OL,20,Fsunny spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
